                      <locus target="#10v #20v #30v #42v #58r #68r #79v #88v #109v #126r #130v #138v" facs="011 021 031 043 058 068 080 089 110 126 131 139">10v, 20v, 30v, 42v, 58r, 68r, 79v, 88v, 109v, 126r, 130v, 138v</locus> (alternating red and black dots across page</decoNote>
